div.p:
Finally, correspondence may be categorized in terms of its
                        object- and/or eventlike nature (e.g. letter, signed personally; telegram;
                        copy; draft) requiring a separate element ct:correspClass.

These elements are all members of a model class called model.correspDescPart;
                    additional features may be defined by defining new elements and adding them to 
                    that class.
